    • Constructor Detail

      • Power

        public Power​(int powerID,
             java.lang.Boolean isActive,
             java.lang.Boolean usableOnPlayerTurn,
             java.lang.Boolean validOnOpponentTurn,
             TurnPhase turnPhase)
        Constructor of Power class.
        Parameters:
        powerID - ID of the power
        isActive - states if the power have to be activated by the player
        usableOnPlayerTurn - indicates if the power can be used during the player's turn
        validOnOpponentTurn - flag that states if the power can be activated during the opponent's turn
        turnPhase - is an enum that indicates in what phase of the game the power can be used
